    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>John Naples-Campbell is an educator. </p>
<p>He graduated with a BA (Hons) Drama and Theatre Arts from Queen Margaret University College in 2004.</p>
<p>For almost 20 years, John has devoted his career to teaching. He's passionate about making classrooms more inclusive and last year was named Educator of the Year at the National Proud Scotland Awards. </p>]]></Value>
